{"id":18821,"date":"2024-01-30T22:03:44","date_gmt":"2021-01-30T16:33:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=18821"},"modified":"2024-10-19T12:56:27","modified_gmt":"2024-10-19T07:26:27","slug":"bed-light-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bed-light-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"8 Luminous Bedroom Bed Light Design Ideas For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Turn your bed into a cosy (ier) spot with these eight radiant bed lighting ideas!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Of all the rooms in a house, the bedroom is the one which deserves the most subtle and varied lighting. From comforting you after a long day at work and creating an atmosphere of love and passion to providing the right kind of ambience for an energetic start to the day \u2014 bed lights play an essential role. When you want to change the look of your bedroom, you might just want to rethink the lights in the space and experience a transformation! While we take you through beautiful and practical examples of bed light design, don\u2019t forget to factor in the colour scheme of your home and the availability of natural light into consideration.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Bright Nightstand Lamp Never Feels Old<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If there are a lot of natural wooden elements in your bedroom, you might want to go with warmer bed lights that can reflect off the natural elements, creating a soothing effect.&nbsp; The bedside lamp works well with the ceiling lights and plenty of natural light streaming in from the windows. You can choose a denser light for the bedside lamp as it will shift the focus towards itself at night as opposed to the window in the daytime.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215834\/nightstand-lamp-bed-light.jpg\" alt=\"Bed light design in minimalist at the bedside looks classic\" class=\"wp-image-18828\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215834\/nightstand-lamp-bed-light.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215834\/nightstand-lamp-bed-light-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215834\/nightstand-lamp-bed-light-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215834\/nightstand-lamp-bed-light-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A classic bedside lamp is a great option for bed lighting<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hanging Side Lamps To Save Table Space!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This kind of bed light design spreads the light evenly, specifically in a room which has a bit darker and antique colour palette. Suspended lighting over the side table can be used to unwind after a hectic day. The hanging bed lights will also open up some space on the table (and ensure that the lights are safe from the shenanigans of clumsy hands!. Hanging lamps come in numerous designs, so you may choose whatever suits the room and you! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215816\/hanging-side-lights-for-bed.jpg\" alt=\"Hanging side led lights for bed in modern style brings a unique charm\" class=\"wp-image-18825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215816\/hanging-side-lights-for-bed.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215816\/hanging-side-lights-for-bed-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215816\/hanging-side-lights-for-bed-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215816\/hanging-side-lights-for-bed-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Modern hanging lamps bring a unique charm to your bedroom design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Designer Hanging Lamps On Either Side<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Elegant hanging lamps work well as a secondary source of light for the bedroom. The lamps are just to illuminate the sides of the bed and provide a complementary design to the room. The lampshade creates a pattern of shadow and light.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215810\/hanging-bed-light-lamp-on-either-side.jpg\" alt=\"Two hanging bed light lamps on each side work well in the bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-18824\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215810\/hanging-bed-light-lamp-on-either-side.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215810\/hanging-bed-light-lamp-on-either-side-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215810\/hanging-bed-light-lamp-on-either-side-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215810\/hanging-bed-light-lamp-on-either-side-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Elegant hanging lamps are a mood!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Chandelier, Reimagined<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For a chic bed light design, you can try modern ceiling lights \u2014 something similar which can ensure sufficient overall lighting for the room. Bed lights on the sides of the bed can be complementary in colour, focused and with a gleaming surface that cuts through the monotone of textures in the room. The bubble-shaped hanging lights here work well as the added layer of bedroom lighting for a quiet evening.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215840\/overhead-hanging-bed-lights-led.jpg\" alt=\"Bubble-shaped hanging led bed lights for modern bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-18829\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215840\/overhead-hanging-bed-lights-led.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215840\/overhead-hanging-bed-lights-led-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215840\/overhead-hanging-bed-lights-led-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215840\/overhead-hanging-bed-lights-led-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Modern overhead lighting for the bed looks pretty and functional<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pastel Palette And Ambidirectional Light Stands<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedrooms are meant to make us feel tranquil and have a welcoming ambience. In such decor, the room would tend to look a bit dull if not properly lit. The light-toned colour palette of the room and the wallpaper allow the light to form a playful shadow on the walls. You can notice that the side tables are not quite crowded, leaving the lamps to have proper space!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215845\/two-bed-lamp-light-stand.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom with two bedside bed light lamps in classic style makes us feel tranquil\" class=\"wp-image-18830\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215845\/two-bed-lamp-light-stand.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215845\/two-bed-lamp-light-stand-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215845\/two-bed-lamp-light-stand-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215845\/two-bed-lamp-light-stand-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Bedside lamps can be a solid bed light source<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bed Lights Like Windchimes<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wherever you want your aesthetic senses to heighten, symmetry never fails. All the lights, including the ceiling-mounted LEDs and the suspended lights, together light up the whole room. The colour scheme of this bedroom is limited to the hues of one colour, tending towards warm, so the yellowish shade in lights makes it even richer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215804\/drop-down-led-light-bed.jpg\" alt=\"Bed with led lights on each side hanging from the ceiling in the yellowish shade lights\" class=\"wp-image-18823\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215804\/drop-down-led-light-bed.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215804\/drop-down-led-light-bed-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215804\/drop-down-led-light-bed-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215804\/drop-down-led-light-bed-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>These drop downlights look and feel great for the bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Play Around With Minimalistic Bed Lights<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The picture is of broad daylight, but imagine having these tiny wall artefacts switched on at night! The rest of the decor in the room, including the colour of the walls, is simple, which draws attention to the lights mounted on the wall. You can pick from a variety of cool wall-mounted lights as per your liking!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215828\/minimalist-led-light-bedside.jpg\" alt=\"Wall-mounted bed lights are designed minimalistic and lends a modern look\" class=\"wp-image-18827\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215828\/minimalist-led-light-bedside.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215828\/minimalist-led-light-bedside-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215828\/minimalist-led-light-bedside-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215828\/minimalist-led-light-bedside-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Minimal bed light designs like these have our heart!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Discard Conventional Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The in-built low shelf behind the bed leaves you with so much space to use. LED light bed lighting options are a smart way to consume less energy and have the area around your bed sufficiently illuminated.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215822\/led-bed-lights-behind-headboard.jpg\" alt=\"The all-white bedroom has bed wall lights behind the bed\" class=\"wp-image-18826\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215822\/led-bed-lights-behind-headboard.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215822\/led-bed-lights-behind-headboard-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215822\/led-bed-lights-behind-headboard-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30215822\/led-bed-lights-behind-headboard-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An LED lights background works as a charming bed lighting option<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There is a lot to think about when it comes to bedroom lighting. Bed lights typically form a part of a second or third layer of lighting for the space, but sometimes it can also be your primary source of lighting! Pick a style that suits your sensibilities, the aesthetics of your bedroom and your practical lighting requirements for the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/romantic-bedroom-lighting-ideas\/\">Romantic Bedroom Lighting Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/home-lightings-and-its-benefits\/\">Home Lighting And Its Benefits<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blo